name: Meekohopanes LoRA
description:
This was a LoRA I wanted to make so I may incorporate it into one of my mixes. It emulates the artist Meekohopanes. This style requires no keywords. I use it at 0.75 weight, but it is also comfortably usable at 0.6-0.8 weight.

I was surprised as to the quality of this LoRA, but it does have a slight saturation issue. I know my VAE works, but you may want to use something other than the orangemix VAE. Or not, I'd just put it into an image editing app and increase the saturation.

All images were generated on AOM3 with Hires fix on.

I also have a Discord. Join if you wanna share results, get advice, or make requests.

Update: Archiving these LoRAs. Though I don't believe it is entirely wrong to copy an artstyle (I use these artstyle LoRAs to make my mixes), I never did ask for permission and honestly, most artists wouldn't say yes.
